US warehouse store giant Costco is seen in Shanghai on Tuesday. The retailer's first store in the Chinese mainland is set to open on August 27 in the Minhang district. The wholesale giant, which operates hundreds of warehouses mainly in the US, also has outlets in Japan and South Korea. Photo: IC   
